node.text:
In honor of the Mambas birthday, here’s the GOAT busting my ass about a decade ago. 

I’ll never forget this night at staples . Kobe hit me with everything in his bag (up & unders, spins baseline & middle, stop & pop behind the screen). Whatever move you name - he had it and there was nothing I could do to stop him. 

Unfortunately he tore his right Achilles toward the end of regulation . But you never would of thought it because he walked it off as if he rolled his ankle . He was that much of a BADASS. We miss you so much Bean. Happy birthday brother - they don’t make em like you no more . Thank you for showing us how to be champions and persevere thru the toughest of times.

node.text:
In honor of the Mambas birthday, here’s the GOAT busting my ass about a decade ago. 

I’ll never forget this night at staples . Kobe hit me with everything in his bag (up & unders, spins baseline & middle, stop & pop behind the screen). Whatever move you name - he had it and there was nothing I could do to stop him. 

Unfortunately he tore his right Achilles toward the end of regulation . But you never would of thought it because he walked it off as if he rolled his ankle . He was that much of a BADASS. We miss you so much Bean. Happy birthday brother - they don’t make em like you no more . Thank you for showing us how to be champions and persevere thru the toughest of times.
